<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style">
<link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:400,700' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
<link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poiret+One' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>




<div class="tophead">
  <head>
  	<title>PetStargram</title>
  </head>
  <div class="logo">
    <h1 class="site-name"><a href="/">PetSTARgram</a></h1></br>
    <h3 class="slogan">The Cutest pets on Instagram!</h3>
  </div>
  <ul id="nav">
    <li><a href="mailto:petstargram@gmail.com">Contact</a></li>
    <li><%= link_to 'Other Pets', other_index_path %></li>
    <li><%= link_to 'Dogs', dog_index_path %></li>
    <li><%= link_to 'Cats', cat_index_path %></li>
  </ul>
</div>

  <div class="register">
    <% if user_signed_in? %>
    <%= link_to "Log Out", destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete %>
    <% else %>
    <!-- LOG IN -->
    <%= link_to "Log In", new_user_session_path%>
    <!-- SIGN UP -->
    <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path%>
    <%end%>
  </div>




<body>
  <div class="rankhome">
    <h1>November Rankings!</h1>
      <div class="cat_container">
        	<a href="http://instagram.com/nala_cat"><img class="cat1" src='http://photos-c.ak.instagram.com/hphotos-ak-xaf1/10632081_749681735098754_1009063030_n.jpg'></a>
        <h4> No.1 Cat! </h4>
        <h4><a href="http://instagram.com/nala_cat">Nala</a></h4>
        <h4><%= @followers %></h4>

        <div class="cat_body">
          <p>Tardar Sauce, AKA Grumpy Cat might be the most popular cat in the media, but in Instagram Nala is the queen. Beating Tardar Sauce by more than four hundred thousand followers,  Nala is the only cat with over one million followers! Looks like she will be getting comfortable up in the number one spot, while other cats go through furious battle of cuteness.</p>
        </div> 
     </div>

    <div class="dog_container">
        <a href="http://instagram.com/marutaro"><img src='http://photos-h.ak.instagram.com/hphotos-ak-xaf1/10655146_741897905870511_1622033811_n.jpg'></a>
        <h4>No.1 Dog!</h4>
        <h4><a href="http://instagram.com/marutaro">Maru</a></h4>
        <div class="dog_body">
          <p>The Japanese Shiba Inu Maru has close to million followers! The 7 year old Maru has a birthday coming up in October, and with Tuna closely chasing him from the no.2 spot, lets see if Maru can keep the crown for his birth month</p>
        </div> 
    </div>


    <div class="other_container">
        <a href="http://instagram.com/bunnymama"><img src='http://photos-h.ak.instagram.com/hphotos-ak-xfa1/10654898_721842437870751_2123901791_n.jpg'></a>
        <h4>No.1 Other Pet!</h4>
        <h4><a href="http://instagram.com/bunnymama">Eddy & Rambo</a></h4>
        <div class="other_body">
          <p>Cats and Dogs aren't the only pets out there. Check out these group of bunnies Eddy, Rambo and Marbee. Eddy, Rambo and Marbee are three cage-free house bunnies that roam around Olive(Owner)'s house armed in cuteness. With army of hedgehogs chasing after them, lets see how long these bunnies could hold the No.1 Spot!
        </div> 
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bottom">
    <div class="video_container">
      <h1>Video of the month!</h1>
      <iframe width="300" height="200" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/ZlOsu870j8E" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        <p>Cat videos are always great! I could literally spend a whole day watching videos after videos! Are you having a grumpy day? Checkout this cat video, I can assure you that it will put a smile on your face and help brighten up your day!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="petofmonth">
      <h1>Pet of the Month!</h1>
      <a href="http://instagram.com/matsumotoooooo"><img src='http://photos-b.ak.instagram.com/hphotos-ak-xaf1/10729395_728954810518033_1244049489_n.jpg'></a>
      <h4>Kinagomu</h4>
      <p>All the way from Japan, Kinagomu's round face is just too adorable! Checkout her instagram page and when you do, make sure to watch the video where drink water off the fountain.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rightbar">
      <div class="doge">
        <% if user_signed_in? %>
        <%= link_to image_tag("http://i.imgur.com/HH5v6mI.png"), new_pet_path %>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <div class="donate">
        <h1>Help the Animals</h4>
       <a href="http://www.aspca.org/"><img src="http://images5.fanpop.com/image/photos/29200000/ASPCA-aspca-29215695-320-240.jpg"></a>
       <h4>Help the animals</h4>
       <p>There are still alot of animals who needs a home and are in need of warm heart to take care of them. Help ASPCA take care of the animals by donating small amount to help spray/neuter and receive vaccination.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="botcont">
    <footer>
      <ul id="botnav">
        <li><%= link_to 'Cats', cat_index_path %></li>
        <li><%= link_to 'Dogs', dog_index_path %></li>
        <li><%= link_to 'Other Pets', other_index_path %></li>
        <li><a href="mailto:petstargram@gmail.com">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </footer>   
  </div>

  <div class="credits">
    <h4>Â©Andy Kim Webdev<img src="http://i.imgur.com/76YYlGb.png"></h4> 
  </div>
    
</body>
</html>
